Eternally here. @MrKimJones continues his #Fendi journey with the #FendiCouture Autumn – Winter 2021 collection - a poetic transfiguration of the past within the present day. Don’t miss the full runway show on Fendi.com.

Artistic Director of Couture and Womenswear: @MrKimJones
Artistic Director of Accessories and Menswear: @SilviaVenturiniFendi
Artistic Director of Jewelry: @delfinadelettrez

Directed by Luca Guadagnino
On Stage Director: @alessiobolzoni
Executive Producer: @emanuela_matranga
Frenesy Executive Producer: Daniela Venturelli
Director of Photography: @rdhardy
Set Design by @studiolucaguadagnino 
Production Designer: @andyhillmanstudio, Laura Pozzaglio
Art director in charge for @studiolucaguadagnino: @giulioghirardistudio
Editors: Marco Costa, Riccardo Giannetti
Music by @maxrichtermusic
Casa di produzione Frenesy Film Company, @lumen_lab
Post Production Facility: @framebyframe_it

Hair: @guidopalau
Make up: @peterphilipsmakeup
Casting: @ShelleyDurkanCasting
Stylist: @alistermackie
 
Location: @cinecittastudios

node.text:
An ode to the Roman landscape, to the eternal beauty of its nature and architecture. Day fades into night as the models twist and turn, mapping the contours of the Palazzo della Civiltà Italiana as the building gradually comes to life in a spectacular, pulsing light show, reminiscent of the tropes of early science fiction cinema.
The soundtrack by Italian composer Alessandro Cortini is a bespoke electronic composition featuring synthesiser tracks inspired by interstellar travel.

Collection by @silviaventurinifendi

Concept and Direction by @nicovascellari
Original soundtrack by @alehan

Styling: @ganio
Hair: @guidopalau
Makeup: @peterphilipsmakeup
Casting: @pg_dmcasting
Filming: @videogang_

node.text:
Drawing from seemingly diverse inspirations, from the visual language of Bernini's marbles to Virgina Woolf's time-travelling, gender-blurring novel Orlando, the show navigates a unique journey from the British Bloomsbury to Rome's Galleria Borghese. 

Stay tuned to discover the full digital experience of the #FendiCouture Part 2

Artistic Director of Couture and Womenswear Collections: @MrKimJones
Artistic Director of Accessories and Menswear Collections: @SilviaVenturiniFendi
Jewellery Creative Director: @delfinadelettrez

Design, direction and production: @bureaubetak @bureaufuture
Music: @maxrichtermusic
Film production: @walterfilms

Hair: @SamMcKnight1
Make up: @PeterPhilipsMakeup
Casting: @ShelleyDurkanCasting

@elliegracecumming
